name: ENCONTRO
description:
"encontro" means "meeting" or "to meet".
it's about the feeling when we finally meet with the ocean, specially after so long, and feel the sea reaching out on our feet (:

encontro was created during pandemic times, so the abstinence of the ocean was represented in this hopeful GIF, manifesting for a soon reencounter (that has already happened!)

may this visual hope bring you calmness 🌊
